  "3195360": {
    "name": "Coromon: Rogue Planet",
    "steam_appid": 3195360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Coromon：流浪星球</strong>将Coromon的策略回合制战斗与Roguelike玩法结合，打造出一款可无限重复游玩的驯兽冒险游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/b6aaa561737377e3fc3ed1ebd9583ebd.webp?t=1759801523\" width=780 height=25 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索超过15种不断变化的生态区域！在穿越Velua星球的旅程中，权衡风险与回报，做出战术决策。每个生态区都拥有独特的故事、新颖的挑战和专属的Coromon生态群。程序生成的地图、遭遇和奖励将确保每次冒险都进展故事并充满新鲜感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/3d57a7e758bde6843a99d0d5cbe088a3.poster.avif?t=1759801523\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/3d57a7e758bde6843a99d0d5cbe088a3.webm?t=1759801523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/fcb5672fad25028885ef584312cf8c45.webp?t=1759801523\" width=780 height=25 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁6位可玩角色，每位都有独特的初始Coromon、背景故事与游戏风格！在探索Farlands荒野的旅途中，你会遇到其他需要帮助的训练师。与他们结盟，将其永久解锁为可选角色，并掌握他们独有的玩法与机制。完成阶段目标还能解锁角色故事，并在未来每次冒险中获得新奖励！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/c86224f6995269548a175cbbb355c718.poster.avif?t=1759801523\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/c86224f6995269548a175cbbb355c718.webm?t=1759801523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/48836b9fe460e29596cedc99aeddfcf9.webp?t=1759801523\" width=780 height=25 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从7只全新初始Coromon中选择其一，然后捕捉、驯服并训练超过130种怪兽！每只Coromon都有主副双属性、性格与技能。与团队协作、提升能力、定制技能组合、强化战斗力——并迎战野生Coromon、训练师、成群敌人、Boss等强敌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/10c41b388a1917f702f1e462162ddc8f.poster.avif?t=1759801523\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/10c41b388a1917f702f1e462162ddc8f.webm?t=1759801523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/4b5f666ab3e46a74343d7b03300a0767.webp?t=1759801523\" width=780 height=25 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在初代<i>Coromon</i>事件之后，一艘神秘外星飞船坠毁在Farlands某处。作为Lux Solis的勇敢战斗探索者，你的任务是追踪飞船，揭示威胁星球的Crimsonite瘟疫之谜！旅途中你将遇到被Crimsonite感染的生物——这是一种危险且不稳定的物质，会感染一切触及之物，包括你的Coromon！务必保护好你的团队，并探索这场灾难背后的外星真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/b3721557332e1d18cedec93e1f074adb.avif?t=1759801523\" width=96 height=111 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/dcf201ada39c3ef23f361a89b02fe5a2.avif?t=1759801523\" width=96 height=111 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/f204cf2caf9b3eeb5795f01cf00d0c88.avif?t=1759801523\" width=96 height=111 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/648d942cbb5c1325dbad3ccc32c9ff07.webp?t=1759801523\" width=780 height=25 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用各类装备与工具提升自身能力！游戏的元进度系统允许你不断强化技能与实力。分配并使用资源来升级前哨站，为每位角色解锁新的技能与能力。想在Farlands生存下来，运气与技巧缺一不可！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/d669750c18b33c4a0295786e9dc35388.poster.avif?t=1759801523\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/d669750c18b33c4a0295786e9dc35388.webm?t=1759801523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/d35295661cec82b57670f71c23a09bb5.webp?t=1759801523\" width=780 height=25 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集资源，推进Lux Solis的太空探索计划！在冒险中，你将收集坠毁外星飞船的残骸碎片。每次带回新信息和资源，Lux Solis不仅会给予额外奖励，你也将与全球玩家携手推进叙事、揭示银河的终极秘密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/002798eaccf69ddf2f767826fe423bd0.poster.avif?t=1759801523\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195360/extras/002798eaccf69ddf2f767826fe423bd0.webm?t=1759801523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
